{"type": "article", "id": 934, "title": "社交网络看太阳升起", "description": "", "date": "2014-05-29T16:13:11Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [{"id": 234, "name": "社交网络"}, {"id": 892, "name": "信息图"}, {"id": 86, "name": "Twitter"}], "category": 12, "column": null, "author": 3, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604214851oD8FvRPN6spVdjzL.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>每天早上看着太阳升起你会说什么？大概不会说什么，拍张照片传到网上大概是更常见的场景——如果你已经脱离睡梦的话。<br>\r\n</p>\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://cartodb.s3.amazonaws.com/static_vizz/sunrise.html?title=true&amp;description=true&amp;search=false&amp;shareable=true&amp;cartodb_logo=true&amp;layer_selector=false&amp;legends=false&amp;scrollwheel=true&amp;sublayer_options=1%7C1&amp;sql=&amp;zoom=2&amp;center_lat=22.917922936146045&amp;center_lon=51.328125#\" target=\"_blank\">这副动态地图</a>可以告诉你，24 小时里，在 Twitter 上用不同语言提到“日出”这个词的位置。昼夜交替线上黄色的闪光基本反应了互联网的覆盖情况——当然，除了中国：<span>（加载可能需要些许时间）</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"640\" frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://cartodb.s3.amazonaws.com/static_vizz/sunrise.html?title=true&amp;description=true&amp;search=false&amp;shareable=true&amp;cartodb_logo=true&amp;layer_selector=false&amp;legends=false&amp;scrollwheel=true&amp;sublayer_options=1%7C1&amp;sql=&amp;zoom=2&amp;center_lat=22.917922936146045&amp;center_lon=51.328125#\">\r\n\t</iframe>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}